parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light remains illuminated
the airbag is protruding out of the dashboard
the airbag is no longer operational.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of recall repairs can leave vehicles with potentially life-threatening defects on the road, putting drivers and passengers at risk.
symptoms: Notification of recall received
but parts are unavailable
manufacturer exceeds a reasonable amount of time for recall repair
dealer claims no issue with airbag system despite warning light illumination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended shifting of the transmission into 3rd gear at high speeds can cause a sudden loss of power and speed, increasing the risk of accidents, especially on highways. The malfunction can also lead to a loss of control, as the vehicle becomes stuck in a single gear.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly shifts into 3rd gear at high speeds
the vehicle gets stuck in 3rd gear
the vehicle's speed is drastically reduced
the transmission fault warning message "Transmission Fault; Limited Gears" appears
the problem resets when the engine is turned off and back on
but reoccurs with greater frequency as the vehicle warms up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the brake pedal to travel to the floorboard, leading to a loss of braking ability, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal travels to the floorboard
the brake warning light illuminates
the vehicle stalls or hesitates
the tire pressure light stays on
the vehicle jumps to the side when hitting a bump.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of control, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle starts and cuts off
the engine hesitates
the vehicle stalls
oil leaks into the valves.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the suspension system can cause the vehicle to lose stability, leading to a loss of control, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The suspension low warning light illuminates
the vehicle jumps to the side when hitting a bump.
